9. Product Objectives

The MVP should successfully demonstrate:

Objective 1

Capture citizen feedback through multiple modalities.

Objective 2

Automatically understand and structure citizen inputs.

Objective 3

Detect recurring community issues.

Objective 4

Combine issues with public datasets.

Objective 5

Generate evidence-backed priority rankings.

Objective 6

Produce explainable decision briefs for MPs.

10. Success Metrics

The prototype will be considered successful if it can:

Functional
Accept multilingual submissions
Analyze images and voice
Cluster similar issues
Produce a ranked list of development priorities
Generate explainable recommendations
Technical
End-to-end processing
Modular architecture
Cloud deployment
AI-driven reasoning
Deterministic scoring
User

An MP should be able to answer three questions within five minutes:

What should I prioritize?
Why should I prioritize it?
What evidence supports this recommendation?
